msgstr "手風琴"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php:376
msgid "Add a drag handle to resize the sidebar width."
msgstr "新增拖曳手把以調整側邊欄寬度。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php:356
msgid "Add a toggle button to collapse and expand the sidebar."
msgstr "新增一個切換按鈕，用於折疊和展開側邊欄。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php:320
msgid ""
"Add interactive controls to the lesson editor sidebar for better workspace "
"management."
msgstr "在課程編輯器側邊欄新增互動式控件，以便更好地管理工作區。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php:128
msgid "Alert"
msgstr "警報"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php:241
msgid ""
"Apply enhanced styling to the lesson viewer including improved header, "
"sidebar appearance, content layout, and visual refinements."
msgstr ""
"對課程檢視器套用增強樣式，包括改進標題、側邊欄外觀、內容版面和視覺優化。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php:169
msgid "Available Blocks"
msgstr "可用區塊"

#: blocks/fca-accordion/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "A customizable accordion component with smooth animations."
msgstr "具有流暢動畫效果的可自訂手風琴元件。"

#: blocks/fca-custom-video-player/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Advanced video player with custom controls and chapter support."
msgstr "高級視訊播放器，支援自訂控制和章節播放。"

#: blocks/fca-list/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Clean icon list with customizable markers."
msgstr "簡潔的圖示列表，帶有可自訂的標記。"

#: blocks/fca-alert/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Display alert messages with different styles (info, warning, success, error)."
msgstr "顯示不同樣式的提示訊息（訊息、警告、成功、錯誤）。"

#: blocks/fca-code/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Display code with syntax highlighting and copy functionality."
msgstr "顯示程式碼時帶有語法高亮和複製功能。"

#: blocks/fca-tabs/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Display content in tabbed sections with horizontal or vertical layout."
msgstr "以分頁形式顯示內容，佈局可水平或垂直。"

#: blocks/fca-download/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Display downloadable files with file type detection and icons."
msgstr "顯示可下載文件，並能辨識文件類型和顯示圖示。"

#: blocks/fca-button/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Displays a customizable button."
msgstr "顯示一個可自訂按鈕。"

#: blocks/fca-image/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Displays a responsive image with optional rounded corners."
msgstr "顯示具有可選圓角的自適應影像。"

#: blocks/fca-card/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Displays content within a styled card container."
msgstr "在樣式化的卡片容器中顯示內容。"

#: blocks/fca-video/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Embed videos with custom controls and styling."
msgstr "嵌入影片時可自訂控制項和樣式。"

#: blocks/fca-callout/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Highlight important information with a callout box."
msgstr "使用標註框突出顯示重要資訊。"

#: blocks/fca-checklist/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Interactive checklist with progress tracking."
msgstr "帶有進度追蹤功能的互動式清單。"

#: blocks/fca-flashcard/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Interactive flashcard with flip animation. Click to reveal the answer."
msgstr "帶有翻頁動畫的互動式單字卡。點選即可顯示答案。"

#: blocks/fca-image-hotspot/block.json:1
msgctxt "block description"
msgid "Interactive image with clickable hotspots that reveal information."
msgstr "具有可點選熱點的互動式圖像，點選熱點即可顯示資訊。"

