#. Description of the plugin
msgid ""
"Custom Gutenberg blocks for Fluent Community course lesson editor. Enables "
"custom blocks that integrate seamlessly with Fluent Community's SPA "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"適用於 Fluent Community 課程編輯器的自訂 Gutenberg 區塊。支援與 Fluent "
"Community 的 SPA 環境無縫整合的自訂區塊。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php:229
